title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 - Dec 29 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 - Dec 29 2021
description:
EIB Guest Host Michael Berry, "The Czar of Talk" from NewsRadio 740 KTRH in Houston, continues his conversation with Dr. Peter A. McCullough on weighing the risks of vaccines for young people versus the risk of the virus itself. Congressman Jim Jordan (R-OH) calls to hold Joe Biden and his regime responsible for doing "everything wrong,” as he pledges to investigate Fauci if the GOP takes back the House.
